OL,3,CDisgraced ex-BBC newsreader Huw
OL,4,CEdwards urged to return his salary
OL,6,FThe Culture Secretary has urged
OL,7,Fdisgraced former BBC newsreader Huw
OL,8,FEdwards to "return his salary" after
OL,9,Fadmitting to having indecent images of
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FLisa Nandy asked the BBC to look into
OL,13,Fwhether it can recoup an estimated
OL,14,F#200,000, which Edwards earned in the
OL,15,Fperiod from his arrest in November
OL,16,Funtil he resigned five months later.
