OL,3,CDisgraced ex-BBC newsreader Huw
OL,4,CEdwards urged to return his salary
OL,6,FEdwards earlier in the week admitted
OL,7,Fmaking indecent photographs, with
OL,8,Fseven of the 41 images being of the
OL,9,Fmost serious type, and the BBC
OL,10,Facknowledged it was aware of his
OL,11,Farrest at the time.
OL,13,FMs Nandy told Sky News that she has
OL,14,Fasked to see the employment law advice
OL,15,Fgiven to the BBC, and called for the
OL,16,Fcorporation's director-general Tim
OL,17,FDavie to address "outstanding issues",
OL,18,Fand come back to her next week.
OL,20,FThe minister also said of Edwards: "I
OL,21,Fthink he ought to return his salary.
