OL,3,CDisgraced ex-BBC newsreader Huw
OL,4,CEdwards urged to return his salary
OL,6,F"I think having been arrested on such
OL,7,Fserious charges all the way back in
OL,8,FNovember, to continue to receive that
OL,9,Fsalary all the way through until he
OL,10,Fresigned is wrong and it's not a good
OL,11,Fuse of taxpayers' money.
OL,13,F"I think most people in the country
OL,14,Fwill agree with that but whether he
OL,15,Fdoes that or not is up to him."
OL,17,FShe added: "I've asked the BBC to look
OL,18,Fat what's possible."
