OL,4,CEdwards urged to return his salary
OL,6,FMs Nandy said she has "ongoing
OL,7,Fconcerns", that the BBC needs
OL,8,F"futureproofing" so that
OL,9,Fwhistleblowers are taken seriously and
OL,10,Fcomplaints are acted upon following
OL,11,Fher meeting with Mr Davie on Thursday.
OL,13,FThe Culture Secretary told BBC Radio 5
OL,14,FLive's Chiles On Friday programme that
OL,15,FMr Davie "recognised there is much
OL,16,Fmore work to do", and explained what
OL,17,Ftypes of questions the BBC needs to
OL,18,Faddress.
