OL,3,CDisgraced ex-BBC newsreader Huw
OL,4,CEdwards urged to return his salary
OL,6,FTwo whistleblowers, one current and
OL,7,Fone former BBC worker, alleged that
OL,8,Fthey received "inappropriate messages"
OL,9,Ffrom Edwards, and expressed
OL,10,Fdisappointment on Thursday to BBC News
OL,11,Fthat an internal inquiry into the
OL,12,Fformer newsreader had not been made
OL,13,Fpublic.
OL,15,FBefore Edwards resigned on medical
OL,16,Fadvice in April, he was the
OL,17,Fbroadcaster's highest-paid newsreader,
OL,18,Fwith a pay bracket between #475,000
OL,19,Fand #479,999 for the year 2023/24,
OL,20,Faccording to the BBC's latest annual
OL,21,Freport.
