OL,3,CDisgraced ex-BBC newsreader Huw
OL,4,CEdwards urged to return his salary
OL,6,FMr Davie defended Edwards' pay rise of
OL,7,F#40,000 compared with 2022/23, when he
OL,8,Fwas paid between #435,000 and #439,999.
OL,10,FHe told BBC News it was made up of an
OL,11,F"inflationary increase", and work the
OL,12,Fveteran broadcaster did at the
OL,13,Fcorporation in February 2023 before
OL,14,Fany allegations were made.
OL,16,FMr Davie said the corporation will
OL,17,F"look at all options" in trying to
OL,18,Freclaim pay from Edwards, but ruled
OL,19,Fout doing the same for his pension due
OL,20,Fto legal reasons.
