OL,6,FExplaining the BBC's decision not to
OL,7,Fgo public with Edwards' arrest, he
OL,8,Fsaid it was following police advice.
OL,10,FMr Davie added: "We thought long and
OL,11,Fhard about this, this wasn't a knee-
OL,12,Fjerk decision.
OL,14,F"And it was difficult but when the
OL,15,Fpolice, if you think about this in
OL,16,Fterms of precedent, people do get
OL,17,Farrested and then we've had situations
OL,18,Fwhere no charges (are made) and
OL,19,Fthere's nothing there to be followed
OL,20,Fup on."
