OL,4,CEdwards urged to return his salary
OL,6,FThe BBC chief maintained that as
OL,7,FEdwards remained suspended before his
OL,8,Fresignation in April "on the basis of
OL,9,Fmedical advice from his doctors",
OL,10,Fthere were no issues relating to BBC
OL,11,Femployees' safety.
OL,13,FWhile he knew the severity of the
OL,14,Fcharges, Mr Davie said he was "very
OL,15,Fshocked", and found the specific
OL,16,Fevidence against Edwards "deeply
OL,17,Fdisturbing".
