OL,4,CEdwards urged to return his salary
OL,6,FThe Department for Culture, Media and
OL,7,FSport (DCMS) said that Ms Nandy is
OL,8,F"like the whole nation, shocked by Huw
OL,9,FEdwards' abhorrent actions, and her
OL,10,Fthoughts are with the victims whose
OL,11,Flives have been destroyed".
OL,13,FShe added it is up to the "judiciary
OL,14,Fto decide on an appropriate sentence".
OL,16,FEdwards looks set to be stripped of
OL,17,Fthe honorary degree he received from
OL,18,FYork St John University in 2019.
